fields.description:

This elliptical silencer is installed with a screwable mount. With EG-BE.
The use of exhausts without dB-killer is not allowed in public traffic.

This product is suitable for the following motorcycles:

R 1200 R (2017 - 2018), 
R 1200 RS (2017 - 2018)

fields.name: Akrapovic Slip-On Line Titanium Rear Silencer
fields.description:
Akrapovic Slip-On Line Titanium Rear Silencer

Designed with a striking resemblance to the Akrapovič exhaust for the Yamaha R1 Superbike, this new version of the EC/ECE type-approved Slip-On Line (Titanium) system is constructed from high-grade lightweight titanium for the link pipe, end cap, and muffler outer sleeve, which is sandblasted for an enhanced appearance. The package also includes a forged carbon-fibre heat shield, which is Akrapovič’s first use of this technology in the motorcycle sector. Producing a deep, full, and vivid sound, the Slip-On Line (Titanium) offers ideal throttle response from its simple plug-and-play installation, which requires no remapping.

This product is suitable for the following motorcycles:
MT-10 (2022), 
MT-10 SP (2022)

fields.name: Akrapovic Slip-On Line Carbon Rear Silencer
fields.description:
Akrapovic Slip-On Line Carbon Rear Silencer

This updated design uses race-proven materials in the construction of the system, with a high-grade lightweight titanium link pipe, titanium inner muffler structure, and new style of end cap all matched to a carbon-fibre outer muffler sleeve, which has created an exhaust that is over 23% lighter than the standard stock version. A full and intense sound is emitted when the machine is idling, offering a deep, full tone with a distinctive Akrapovič character when on the move.
The Akrapovič Slip-On Line (Carbon) exhaust upgrade is achievable through a combination of two choices of optional headers – titanium and stainless steel – which are available with an optional noise insert for those who want to combine the system with the headers.

This product is suitable for the following motorcycles:

S 1000 R (2021 - 2022)

fields.name: WILBERS LDC Nivomat suspension kit RFLHRXS Road King Special FL3, 2019
fields.description:
Wilbers LDC Nivomat suspension kit
The Wilbers LDC shock offers excellent comfort in all conditions. It adjusts to the different loading conditions without any intervention, completely automatically - without buttons and without electronics! After the pillion passenger has taken a seat with or without luggage, the deeply slumped chassis pumps itself back up to the defined ride level after a few meters of travel by the shock absorber delivering additional oil into its cylinder through its own stroke movement. The resulting increase in pressure also leads to an adjustment of the damping.

Suspension kit includes:
Nivomat, 
Ecoline shock, 
Zero friction fork springs, 
Fork oil.

fields.name: Shad SH36 Side Cases
fields.description:
Shad SH36 Side Cases

SH36 Carbon side cases stand out for their innovative and functional design. The cutting-edge technology and innovative design of the SH36 received the prestigious Reddot Design Award 2015, a reference among designers and manufacturers in the industry. They also won the German Design Award Special 2017. Its innovative shapes create trends and offer an elegant, sophisticated and modern design, characterized by aerodynamic lines and carefully designed aesthetic details. The SH36 side cases with carbon look perfectly match the SH58X, SH48 or SH39 top cases.

Features:

Frame structure that provides waterproofing, rigidity and lightness, 
Additional locking cylinder included to lock the side cases and top case with a common key, 
Luggage strap to secure the load, 
Handle Lock System: locks the cases and locks them to the motorcycle, 
Handle for easy carrying, 
Open and close with one hand, no key needed, 
The key is only needed to lock the cases to the motorcycle, 
Change Colour System covers available, 
Patented 3P System is used for mounting (not included), 
Integrated design: by eliminating the typical rectangular frame and reducing it to just one arm in the shape of a horizontal "L", the mount is much better integrated into the motorcycle, 
Position: all the weight is supported as far as possible towards the center of gravity of the motorcycle, resulting in more safety and stability while riding, 
Flexible anchorage: the 3P System provides greater safety and stability while riding, thanks to a slight oscillation of the cases, which allows the air to better flow around them

fields.name: Garmin zumo XT Navigation System
fields.description:
Garmin zumo XT Navigation System

The rugged zūmo® XT all terrain motorcycle navigator is built for adventure.

Its ultrabright 5.5” display is glove friendly and rain resistant. It can withstand all kinds of weather, extreme temperatures and vibrations. Get adventurous routes with turn by turn directions for on road navigation and topographic or BirdsEye Satellite Imagery for off road guidance no subscription needed. Rider alerts help prepare you for sharp curves and railroad crossings. Easily manage and review routes, tracks and waypoints across your navigator, smartphone and computer using Garmin Explore™. Pair with a compatible inReach® satellite communicator (sold separately) for interactive SOS, two way messaging and location sharing.

Features:

Ultra bright 5.5 inch HD touch display, 
Road navigation maps for Europe including updates, 
pre-installed topographic maps for terrain navigation, 
BirdsEye satellite images via download included, 
Garmin AdventurousRouting™, 
Round trip, route planning and TracBack function integrated, 
Live weather, live traffic and more via Garmin Drive App, 
TripAdvisor®, Foursquare®, iOverlander™ and motorcycle POIs, 
Bluetooth® hands-free function and integrated music player, 
Integrated track recorder with compass and altitude profile, 
Garmin ExploreApp compatible, 
Compatible with inReach® devices (sold separately).

fields.name: Sena 5S FC-Moto Edition Bluetooth Communication System Single Pack
fields.description:
Sena 5S Bluetooth Communication System Single Pack

Born from the legendary Sena SMH5, the Sena 5S is the next-generation of feature-rich and value-packed intercoms from Sena. With this easy to use and accessible unit, you get High Definition in-helmet speakers, High Definition two-way intercom, and integrated LCD screen; all the features you need at an amazing value. The 5S with Bluetooth® 5 keeps you connected to your riding companion or passenger with HD Sound quality, music sharing, and audio equalizer profiles built right in. With even more features packed in, it also lets you answer phone calls hands-free, listen to FM Radio, and hear your GPS prompts. The 5S features a Helmet Clamp Kit and Boom Microphone. The Jog Dial makes for an intuitive user interface that is much easier to control while riding, which means you'll ride safer.

Features:

2-way intercom, 
HD speakers, 
HD intercom, 
Multi-language voice command, 
Ergonomic shape, 
LCD display, 
FM radio, 
Bluetooth® 5, 
Headset Profile (HSP), 
Hands-Free Profile (HFP), 
Advanced Audio Distribution Profile (A2DP), 
Audio Video Remote Control Profile (AVRCP), 
Noise Cancellation via Advanced Noise Control™, 
Specifications:

Working Distance: Up to 700 m (0.4 mi) in open terrain, 
Radio frequency specifications: 76 ~ 108MHz, 
Codec: Built-in SBC Codec, 
USB-C connection, 
Talk time: 7 hours, 
Charging time: 1.5 hours, 
Lithium Polymer Battery, 
Operating temperature: -10˚C to 55˚C (14°F ~ 131°F).

The 50C is packed with features, including Sena's best-in-class mesh and Bluetooth communication technology and 4K camera capabilities, as well as an all-new SOUND BY Harman Kardon speaker & microphone. The 50C's new speakers and SOUND BY Harman Kardon microphone provide an unparalleled audio experience on your trip.

fields.name: MIDLAND H9 4K Ultra HD Action Camera

The MIDLAND Action Camera H9 is the first of its kind. It takes videos and sound - and even photos - with high resolution. The MIDLAND Action Camera H9 with its numerous functions is ideal for all outdoor activities - including remote control, waterproof housing, self-timer and image stabilizer. The image quality can be adjusted as needed (eg exposure). For extra long shots on tours, the battery is replaceable.

Features:

Ultra HD 4K video camera (Ambarella A12 chip), 
Resolution: 4K @ 30fps / 2.7K@30fps / 1080p @ 30 / 60fps / 720p @ 120fps,
